g/dictionary/index.asp?action=view&amp;term_id=11488&amp;term_type_id=1&amp;term_type_text=People&amp;letter=F" rel="nofollow">http://www.wisconsinhistory.org/dictionary/index.asp?action=view&amp;term_id=11488&amp;term_type_id=1&amp;term_type_text=People&amp;letter=F</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2008-07-27</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Freethinkers+in+Wisconsin&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.date=2008&amp;rft.pub=Dictionary+of+Wisconsin+History&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wisconsinhistory.org%2Fdictionary%2Findex.asp%3Faction%3Dview%26term_id%3D11488%26term_type_id%3D1%26term_type_text%3DPeople%26letter%3DF&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Freethought"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-4"><b><a href="#cite_ref-4" title="">^</a></b> Demerath, N. J. III and Victor Thiessen, "On Spitting Against the Wind: Organizational Precariousness and American Irreligion," <i>The American Journal of Sociology</i>, 71: 6 (May, 1966), 674-687.</li>
<li id="cite_note-5"><b><a href="#cite_ref-5" title="">^</a></b> Demerath, N. J. III and Victor Thiessen, "On Spitting Against the Wind: Organizational Precariousness and American Irreligion," <i>The American Journal of Sociology</i>, 71: 6 (May, 1966), 674-687.</li>
<li id="cite_note-Sauk_County_Freethinkers-6">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Sauk_County_Freethinkers_6-0" title=""><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Sauk_County_Freethinkers_6-1" title=""><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web"><a href="http://www.freecongregation.org/History/Free%20Congregation/index.html" class="external text" title="http://www.freecongregation.org/History/Free%20Congregation/index.html" rel="nofollow">"History of the Free Congregation of Sauk County: The "Freethinkers" Story"</a>. Free Congregation of Sauk County. April, 2007<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.freecongregation.org/History/Free%20Congregation/index.html" class="external free" title="http://www.freecongregation.org/History/Free%20Congregation/index.html" rel="nofollow">http://www.freecongregation.org/History/Free%20Congregation/index.html</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2008-07-27</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=History+of+the+Free+Congregation+of+Sauk+County%3A+The+%22Freethinkers%22+Story&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.date=April%2C+2007&amp;rft.pub=Free+Congregation+of+Sauk+County&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.freecongregation.org%2FHistory%2FFree%2520Congregation%2Findex.html&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Freethought"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-7"><b><a href="#cite_ref-7" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web"><a href="http://ffrf.org/fttoday/2002/junejuly02/gascho.php" class="external text" title="http://ffrf.org/fttoday/2002/junejuly02/gascho.php" rel="nofollow">"The Turners, Forty-eighters and Freethinkers"</a>. Freedom from Religion Foundation. July, 2002<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://ffrf.org/fttoday/2002/junejuly02/gascho.php" class="external free" title="http://ffrf.org/fttoday/2002/junejuly02/gascho.php" rel="nofollow">http://ffrf.org/fttoday/2002/junejuly02/gascho.php</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2008-07-27</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=The+Turners%2C+Forty-eighters+and+Freethinkers&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.date=July%2C+2002&amp;rft.pub=Freedom+from+Religion+Foundation&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fffrf.org%2Ffttoday%2F2002%2Fjunejuly02%2Fgascho.php&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Freethought"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
